profile:
Luna's boyfriend, he has decided not to engage in premarital
relations, so they have a platonic relationship. As a hunter, he is an
adventurer with average abilities and his weapon of choice is the bow
and arrow.

name: Dalton
profile:
A chubby and lecherous middle-aged adventurer based in the slums. In
the forest dungeon, his large axe is effective, making him a reliable
mercenary.

name: Arashi
profile:
An adventurer who came to this island for women and money, based at
the village inn. As a swordsman, he has experience in dungeon
exploration and is a dependable mercenary.

name: Bob
profile:
An adventurer of the heavyweight class who doesn't carry unnecessary
weapons, relying solely on his strength. He can destroy even rocks
that obstruct progress with his incredible physical power, making him
a beast-like mercenary.

name: Shouta
profile:
A boy who dreams of becoming the world's greatest adventurer and
admires the boss who leads his underlings, based in the village. His
small stature allows him to pass through narrow shortcuts, making him
a useful mercenary.

name: Country Girl
profile:
A shy girl who makes her living gathering medicinal herbs and
compounding them. She met \N[2] when she requested an escort to the
forest.
